<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>unfired dye vial <br>
prism <br>
jar of lacquer <br>
quality firing sheet <br>
<br>
you need to combine the vial and quality firing sheet in a kiln (trivial is higher than 53) I made 19 out of 33 tries at skill levels 49 - 53, still was not trivial at 53. Then you combine the prism and lacquer in a brew barrel (this is trivial at 54). Then you take the vial you made in the first step, and the dye you made in the second step and combine them in a brew barrel to make the final product (it was not trivial at 56).<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
<br>
To sum in up:<br>
Unfired Dye Vial + Quality Firing Sheet + Kiln = Dye Vial<br>
Glaze Lacquer + Prism Shard + Brew Barrel = Prismatic Dye<br>
Dye Vial + Prismatic Dye + Brew Barrel = Vial of Prysmatic Dye<br>
<br>
Trivials all less that 150ish, total cost per is about 30pp with 130+ cha. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=204546" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.marksmans.com/images/xalsig.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pissed1vi2soe@themagicianstower>Pissed1VI2SOE</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sage</span><br>  Posts: 628<br> <font color=#333333>(2/25/03 12:19 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowergeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8884.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_exclamation_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Making Armor Dyes</span><hr size=1> Jooooooo Roxxors<br>
